  "detailed_description": "游戏官方讨论群：993890935<br>QQ频道：<br>你可以在这里找到我，进行BUG反馈并得到优先内测的资格。<br><br><strong>本作特色</strong><br>引人入胜的三十万字的精彩剧情；<br>同时照顾核心玩家与非核心玩家的难易度；<br>深度的战斗系统，与特殊的额外挑战；<br>特殊的道具系统、可以自由组合的符文系统、丰富的技能设定，加上可以改变技能性质的特性设定，使得战术拥有无限种可能！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/17bd814cc2427c17895f127eff203e0d.poster.avif?t=1661722807\" width=608 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/17bd814cc2427c17895f127eff203e0d.webm?t=1661722807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/17bd814cc2427c17895f127eff203e0d.mp4?t=1661722807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>开发者</strong><br>《列传：革新战争》是灰烬游戏工作室出品的第一款游戏。<br>工作室由什么都做的工具人灰烬以及平面美术担当铅笔构成。<br>是我们用业余时间去制作，一共打磨了三年的自信作，希望大家能够喜欢。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/0a6a22a0e1f7fe7cf085ed8013356571.poster.avif?t=1661722807\" width=512 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/0a6a22a0e1f7fe7cf085ed8013356571.webm?t=1661722807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/0a6a22a0e1f7fe7cf085ed8013356571.mp4?t=1661722807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏简介</strong><br>列传革新战争是一款传统却不失革新的策略战棋类游戏，考验玩家的策略与智慧。<br>本作以中世纪为游戏背景，玩家可以在这里体验到“王道中的邪道”式新颖故事，故事拥有丰富的人物，所有角色都具有自己的魅力——<br>包括反派，无一例外。<br>在故事中玩家将扮演主角玛斯塔奇在幻想中世纪进行冒险；<br>故事将从冒险团的设立开始，一步步招募新的成员；<br>在意外中参与国家纷争，最终在机缘巧合下担负了拯救世界的重任。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/faa63473f7856f9e30a208b836af7ad3.poster.avif?t=1661722807\" width=608 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/faa63473f7856f9e30a208b836af7ad3.webm?t=1661722807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387590/extras/faa63473f7856f9e30a208b836af7ad3.mp4?t=1661722807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
